node.title: Major slip closes Wellington train line
node.description: Metlink says its trains cannot travel north of Plimmerton because of a slip between Pukerua Bay and Paekakariki.
node.content:
["A major slip has forced the cancellation of train services between Wellington and the Kapiti Coast.", "", "
\nPhoto: 123rf\n
", "Metlink says its trains cannot travel north of Plimmerton because of a slip between Pukerua Bay and Paekakariki.", "It is replacing its services betweeen Plimmerton and Waikanae with buses.", "Last week a train struck a landslide in the same area, closing the tracks temporarily and prompting speed restrictions on the line this week."]
